{
  "video_id": "JrJJxn-gCdo",
  "title": "Gavin Schmidt: The emergent patterns of climate change",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12864.0,
      "end_time": 15187.0,
      "text": "We live in a very complex environment:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15187.0,
      "end_time": 17910.0,
      "text": "complexity and dynamism"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17910.0,
      "end_time": 19154.0,
      "text": "and patterns of evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19154.0,
      "end_time": 22390.0,
      "text": "from satellite photographs, from videos."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22390.0,
      "end_time": 25500.0,
      "text": "You can even see it outside your window."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25500.0,
      "end_time": 28910.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s endlessly complex, but somehow familiar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28910.0,
      "end_time": 30870.0,
      "text": "but the patterns kind of repeat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30870.0,
      "end_time": 33360.0,
      "text": "but they never repeat exactly."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33360.0,
      "end_time": 37487.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a huge challenge to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37487.0,
      "end_time": 39619.0,
      "text": "The patterns that you see"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39619.0,
      "end_time": 43339.0,
      "text": "are there at all of the different scales,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43339.0,
      "end_time": 46245.0,
      "text": "but you can&#39;t chop it into one little bit and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46245.0,
      "end_time": 48907.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, well let me just make a smaller climate.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48908.0,
      "end_time": 53120.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t use the normal products of reductionism"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53120.0,
      "end_time": 55842.0,
      "text": "to get a smaller and smaller thing that I can study"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55842.0,
      "end_time": 58150.0,
      "text": "in a laboratory and say, \"Oh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58150.0,
      "end_time": 60546.0,
      "text": "now that&#39;s something I now understand.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60546.0,
      "end_time": 63913.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the whole or it&#39;s nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63913.0,
      "end_time": 66465.0,
      "text": "The different scales that give you"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66465.0,
      "end_time": 68587.0,
      "text": "these kinds of patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68587.0,
      "end_time": 72440.0,
      "text": "range over an enormous range of magnitude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72440.0,
      "end_time": 74460.0,
      "text": "roughly 14 orders of magnitude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74460.0,
      "end_time": 76951.0,
      "text": "from the small microscopic particles"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76951.0,
      "end_time": 79327.0,
      "text": "that seed clouds"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79327.0,
      "end_time": 81887.0,
      "text": "to the size of the planet itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81887.0,
      "end_time": 83163.0,
      "text": "from 10 to the minus six"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83163.0,
      "end_time": 84240.0,
      "text": "to 10 to the eight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84240.0,
      "end_time": 86532.0,
      "text": "14 orders of spatial magnitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86532.0,
      "end_time": 89943.0,
      "text": "In time, from milliseconds to millennia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89943.0,
      "end_time": 92998.0,
      "text": "again around 14 orders of magnitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92998.0,
      "end_time": 94385.0,
      "text": "What does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94385.0,
      "end_time": 96324.0,
      "text": "Okay, well if you think about how"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96324.0,
      "end_time": 98984.0,
      "text": "you can calculate these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98984.0,
      "end_time": 100943.0,
      "text": "you can take what you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100944.0,
      "end_time": 101970.0,
      "text": "okay, I&#39;m going to chop it up"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 101970.0,
      "end_time": 103349.0,
      "text": "into lots of little boxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103349.0,
      "end_time": 105704.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the result of physics, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105704.0,
      "end_time": 107428.0,
      "text": "And if I think about a weather model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107429.0,
      "end_time": 109923.0,
      "text": "that spans about five orders of magnitude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109923.0,
      "end_time": 113500.0,
      "text": "from the planet to a few kilometers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113500.0,
      "end_time": 114588.0,
      "text": "and the time scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114588.0,
      "end_time": 119000.0,
      "text": "from a few minutes to 10 days, maybe a month."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 119000.0,
      "end_time": 120395.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re interested in more than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 120395.0,
      "end_time": 121700.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re interested in the climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 121700.0,
      "end_time": 123841.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s years, that&#39;s millennia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123841.0,
      "end_time": 126413.0,
      "text": "and we need to go to even smaller scales."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 126414.0,
      "end_time": 128150.0,
      "text": "The stuff that we can&#39;t resolve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 128139.99999999999,
      "end_time": 129978.99999999999,
      "text": "the sub-scale processes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 129979.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131959.0,
      "text": "we need to approximate in some way."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131960.0,
      "end_time": 133722.0,
      "text": "That is a huge challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133722.0,
      "end_time": 135910.0,
      "text": "Climate models in the 1990s"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 135910.0,
      "end_time": 137880.0,
      "text": "took an even smaller chunk of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 137880.0,
      "end_time": 139898.0,
      "text": "only about three orders of magnitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 139898.0,
      "end_time": 141993.0,
      "text": "Climate models in the 2010s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 141993.0,
      "end_time": 143767.0,
      "text": "kind of what we&#39;re working with now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 143767.0,
      "end_time": 146707.0,
      "text": "four orders of magnitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 146707.0,
      "end_time": 149100.0,
      "text": "We have 14 to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 149100.0,
      "end_time": 151209.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re increasing our capability"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 151210.0,
      "end_time": 153800.0,
      "text": "of simulating those at about"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 153800.0,
      "end_time": 156626.0,
      "text": "one extra order of magnitude every decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 156626.0,
      "end_time": 158521.0,
      "text": "One extra order of magnitude in space"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 158521.0,
      "end_time": 161769.0,
      "text": "is 10,000 times more calculations."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 161770.0,
      "end_time": 164150.0,
      "text": "And we keep adding more things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 164150.0,
      "end_time": 166524.0,
      "text": "more questions to these different models."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 166524.0,
      "end_time": 169257.0,
      "text": "So what does a climate model look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 169257.0,
      "end_time": 171598.0,
      "text": "This is an old climate model, admittedly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 171598.0,
      "end_time": 175678.0,
      "text": "a punch card, a single line of Fortran code."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175678.0,
      "end_time": 177656.0,
      "text": "We no longer use punch cards."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 177656.0,
      "end_time": 179897.0,
      "text": "We do still use Fortran."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 179897.0,
      "end_time": 181853.0,
      "text": "New-fangled ideas like C"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 181854.0,
      "end_time": 185890.0,
      "text": "really haven&#39;t had a big impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 185890.0,
      "end_time": 187456.0,
      "text": "on the climate modeling community."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 187456.0,
      "end_time": 188856.0,
      "text": "But how do we go about doing it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 188856.0,
      "end_time": 193480.0,
      "text": "How do we go from that complexity that you saw"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193480.0,
      "end_time": 196100.0,
      "text": "to a line of code?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196100.0,
      "end_time": 197583.0,
      "text": "We do it one piece at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 197583.0,
      "end_time": 199460.0,
      "text": "This is a picture of sea ice"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 199461.0,
      "end_time": 201559.0,
      "text": "taken flying over the Arctic."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 201559.0,
      "end_time": 203597.0,
      "text": "We can look at all of the different equations"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 203597.0,
      "end_time": 206709.0,
      "text": "that go into making the ice grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 206709.0,
      "end_time": 208823.0,
      "text": "or melt or change shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 208823.0,
      "end_time": 209954.0,
      "text": "We can look at the fluxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 209954.0,
      "end_time": 211906.0,
      "text": "We can look at the rate at which"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 211906.0,
      "end_time": 214751.0,
      "text": "snow turns to ice, and we can code that."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 214751.0,
      "end_time": 217800.0,
      "text": "We can encapsulate that in code."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 217800.0,
      "end_time": 218306.0,
      "text": "These models are around"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 218306.0,
      "end_time": 220389.0,
      "text": "a million lines of code at this point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 220389.0,
      "end_time": 223859.0,
      "text": "and growing by tens of thousands of lines of code"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223859.0,
      "end_time": 225500.0,
      "text": "every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 225500.0,
      "end_time": 226703.0,
      "text": "So you can look at that piece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 226703.0,
      "end_time": 228625.0,
      "text": "but you can look at the other pieces too."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 228625.0,
      "end_time": 230558.0,
      "text": "What happens when you have clouds?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 230558.0,
      "end_time": 232716.0,
      "text": "What happens when clouds form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 232717.0,
      "end_time": 234599.0,
      "text": "when they dissipate, when they rain out?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 234599.0,
      "end_time": 236340.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s another piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 236341.0,
      "end_time": 238187.0,
      "text": "What happens when we have radiation"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 238187.0,
      "end_time": 240721.0,
      "text": "coming from the sun, going through the atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 240721.0,
      "end_time": 242647.0,
      "text": "being absorbed and reflected?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 242647.0,
      "end_time": 246626.0,
      "text": "We can code each of those very small pieces as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 246626.0,
      "end_time": 248420.0,
      "text": "There are other pieces:"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 248420.0,
      "end_time": 251502.0,
      "text": "the winds changing the ocean currents."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 251502.0,
      "end_time": 255272.0,
      "text": "We can talk about the role of vegetation"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 255272.0,
      "end_time": 257601.0,
      "text": "in transporting water from the soils"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 257601.0,
      "end_time": 259570.0,
      "text": "back into the atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 259570.0,
      "end_time": 262484.0,
      "text": "And each of these different elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 262484.0,
      "end_time": 266108.0,
      "text": "we can encapsulate and put into a system."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266108.0,
      "end_time": 271256.0,
      "text": "Each of those pieces ends up adding to the whole."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 271256.0,
      "end_time": 273553.0,
      "text": "And you get something like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 273553.0,
      "end_time": 276401.0,
      "text": "You get a beautiful representation"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 276401.0,
      "end_time": 279230.0,
      "text": "of what&#39;s going on in the climate system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 279230.0,
      "end_time": 282412.0,
      "text": "where each and every one of those"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 282412.0,
      "end_time": 285193.0,
      "text": "emergent patterns that you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 285194.0,
      "end_time": 287197.0,
      "text": "the swirls in the Southern Ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 287197.0,
      "end_time": 289953.0,
      "text": "the tropical cyclone in the Gulf of Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 289953.0,
      "end_time": 291594.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s two more that are going to pop up"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 291594.0,
      "end_time": 293948.0,
      "text": "in the Pacific at any point now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 293948.0,
      "end_time": 296661.0,
      "text": "those rivers of atmospheric water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 296661.0,
      "end_time": 299518.0,
      "text": "all of those are emergent properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 299518.0,
      "end_time": 301642.0,
      "text": "that come from the interactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 301642.0,
      "end_time": 305137.0,
      "text": "of all of those small-scale processes I mentioned."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 305137.0,
      "end_time": 307420.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no code that says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 307420.0,
      "end_time": 308899.0,
      "text": "\"Do a wiggle in the Southern Ocean.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 308899.0,
      "end_time": 311567.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no code that says, \"Have two"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 311567.0,
      "end_time": 314465.0,
      "text": "tropical cyclones that spin around each other.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 314465.0,
      "end_time": 318277.0,
      "text": "All of those things are emergent properties."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 318277.0,
      "end_time": 320423.0,
      "text": "This is all very good. This is all great."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 320423.0,
      "end_time": 321693.0,
      "text": "But what we really want to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 321693.0,
      "end_time": 323642.0,
      "text": "is what happens to these emergent properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 323642.0,
      "end_time": 325347.0,
      "text": "when we kick the system?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 325347.0,
      "end_time": 328880.0,
      "text": "When something changes, what happens to those properties?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 328880.0,
      "end_time": 331869.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s lots of different ways to kick the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 331869.0,
      "end_time": 333902.0,
      "text": "There are wobbles in the Earth&#39;s orbit"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 333902.0,
      "end_time": 335781.0,
      "text": "over hundreds of thousands of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 335781.0,
      "end_time": 337807.0,
      "text": "that change the climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 337807.0,
      "end_time": 339943.0,
      "text": "There are changes in the solar cycles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 339943.0,
      "end_time": 343480.0,
      "text": "every 11 years and longer, that change the climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 343480.0,
      "end_time": 346622.0,
      "text": "Big volcanoes go off and change the climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 346622.0,
      "end_time": 349860.0,
      "text": "Changes in biomass burning, in smoke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 349860.0,
      "end_time": 351723.0,
      "text": "in aerosol particles, all of those things"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 351723.0,
      "end_time": 353545.0,
      "text": "change the climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 353545.0,
      "end_time": 357604.0,
      "text": "The ozone hole changed the climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 357604.0,
      "end_time": 359820.0,
      "text": "Deforestation changes the climate"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 359821.0,
      "end_time": 361747.0,
      "text": "by changing the surface properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 361747.0,
      "end_time": 363737.0,
      "text": "and how water is evaporated"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 363737.0,
      "end_time": 366203.0,
      "text": "and moved around in the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 366203.0,
      "end_time": 368488.0,
      "text": "Contrails change the climate"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 368488.0,
      "end_time": 371355.0,
      "text": "by creating clouds where there were none before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 371355.0,
      "end_time": 375953.0,
      "text": "and of course greenhouse gases change the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 375953.0,
      "end_time": 378974.0,
      "text": "Each of these different kicks"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 378974.0,
      "end_time": 381125.0,
      "text": "provides us with a target"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 381125.0,
      "end_time": 383960.0,
      "text": "to evaluate whether we understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 383960.0,
      "end_time": 386121.0,
      "text": "something about this system."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 386121.0,
      "end_time": 388513.0,
      "text": "So we can go to look at"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 388513.0,
      "end_time": 391217.0,
      "text": "what model skill is."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 391217.0,
      "end_time": 393250.0,
      "text": "Now I use the word \"skill\" advisedly:"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 393250.0,
      "end_time": 395661.0,
      "text": "Models are not right or wrong; they&#39;re always wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 395661.0,
      "end_time": 397381.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re always approximations."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 397381.0,
      "end_time": 399275.0,
      "text": "The question you have to ask"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 399275.0,
      "end_time": 402354.0,
      "text": "is whether a model tells you more information"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 402354.0,
      "end_time": 404279.0,
      "text": "than you would have had otherwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 404279.0,
      "end_time": 407659.0,
      "text": "If it does, it&#39;s skillful."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 407660.0,
      "end_time": 410114.0,
      "text": "This is the impact of the ozone hole"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 410114.0,
      "end_time": 412974.0,
      "text": "on sea level pressure, so low pressure, high pressures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 412974.0,
      "end_time": 415569.0,
      "text": "around the southern oceans, around Antarctica."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 415569.0,
      "end_time": 417482.0,
      "text": "This is observed data."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 417482.0,
      "end_time": 419570.0,
      "text": "This is modeled data."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 419570.0,
      "end_time": 421164.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a good match"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 421164.0,
      "end_time": 423115.0,
      "text": "because we understand the physics"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 423115.0,
      "end_time": 426253.0,
      "text": "that controls the temperatures in the stratosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 426253.0,
      "end_time": 427998.0,
      "text": "and what that does to the winds"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 427999.0,
      "end_time": 430180.0,
      "text": "around the southern oceans."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 430180.0,
      "end_time": 431699.0,
      "text": "We can look at other examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 431699.0,
      "end_time": 434555.0,
      "text": "The eruption of Mount Pinatubo in 1991"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 434555.0,
      "end_time": 437354.0,
      "text": "put an enormous amount of aerosols, small particles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 437354.0,
      "end_time": 438941.0,
      "text": "into the stratosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 438941.0,
      "end_time": 442870.0,
      "text": "That changed the radiation balance of the whole planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 442880.0,
      "end_time": 444870.0,
      "text": "There was less energy coming in than there was before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 444870.0,
      "end_time": 446528.0,
      "text": "so that cooled the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 446528.0,
      "end_time": 448547.0,
      "text": "and those red lines and those green lines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 448547.0,
      "end_time": 451112.0,
      "text": "those are the differences between what we expected"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 451112.0,
      "end_time": 452800.0,
      "text": "and what actually happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 452800.0,
      "end_time": 454583.0,
      "text": "The models are skillful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 454583.0,
      "end_time": 456276.0,
      "text": "not just in the global mean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 456276.0,
      "end_time": 459320.0,
      "text": "but also in the regional patterns."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 459320.0,
      "end_time": 462159.0,
      "text": "I could go through a dozen more examples:"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 462160.0,
      "end_time": 465100.0,
      "text": "the skill associated with solar cycles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 465100.0,
      "end_time": 467800.0,
      "text": "changing the ozone in the stratosphere;"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 467800.0,
      "end_time": 469426.0,
      "text": "the skill associated with orbital changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 469427.0,
      "end_time": 471483.0,
      "text": "over 6,000 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 471483.0,
      "end_time": 473881.0,
      "text": "We can look at that too, and the models are skillful."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 473881.0,
      "end_time": 476974.0,
      "text": "The models are skillful in response to the ice sheets"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 476975.0,
      "end_time": 478495.0,
      "text": "20,000 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 478495.0,
      "end_time": 480166.0,
      "text": "The models are skillful"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 480166.0,
      "end_time": 483700.0,
      "text": "when it comes to the 20th-century trends"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 483700.0,
      "end_time": 484585.0,
      "text": "over the decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 484585.0,
      "end_time": 486866.0,
      "text": "Models are successful at modeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 486867.0,
      "end_time": 489472.0,
      "text": "lake outbursts into the North Atlantic"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 489472.0,
      "end_time": 491236.0,
      "text": "8,000 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 491237.0,
      "end_time": 494327.0,
      "text": "And we can get a good match to the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 495463.0,
      "end_time": 497850.0,
      "text": "Each of these different targets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 497850.0,
      "end_time": 499980.0,
      "text": "each of these different evaluations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 499980.0,
      "end_time": 502371.0,
      "text": "leads us to add more scope"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 502371.0,
      "end_time": 503522.0,
      "text": "to these models,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 503522.0,
      "end_time": 506266.0,
      "text": "and leads us to more and more"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 506266.0,
      "end_time": 510254.0,
      "text": "complex situations that we can ask"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 510254.0,
      "end_time": 512823.0,
      "text": "more and more interesting questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 512823.0,
      "end_time": 515533.0,
      "text": "like, how does dust from the Sahara,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 515533.0,
      "end_time": 517267.0,
      "text": "that you can see in the orange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 517267.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520710.00000000006,
      "text": "interact with tropical cyclones in the Atlantic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 520710.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524187.00000000006,
      "text": "How do organic aerosols from biomass burning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 524187.0,
      "end_time": 526910.0,
      "text": "which you can see in the red dots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 526910.0,
      "end_time": 529843.0,
      "text": "intersect with clouds and rainfall patterns?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 529844.0,
      "end_time": 531631.0,
      "text": "How does pollution, which you can see"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 531631.0,
      "end_time": 535530.0,
      "text": "in the white wisps of sulfate pollution in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 535530.0,
      "end_time": 538865.0,
      "text": "how does that affect the temperatures at the surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 538865.0,
      "end_time": 542353.0,
      "text": "and the sunlight that you get at the surface?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 542353.0,
      "end_time": 545841.0,
      "text": "We can look at this across the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 545841.0,
      "end_time": 549501.0,
      "text": "We can look at the pollution from China."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 549501.0,
      "end_time": 553980.0,
      "text": "We can look at the impacts of storms"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 553990.0,
      "end_time": 556543.0,
      "text": "on sea salt particles in the atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 556543.0,
      "end_time": 559104.0,
      "text": "We can see the combination"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 559104.0,
      "end_time": 561275.0,
      "text": "of all of these different things"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 561275.0,
      "end_time": 562742.0,
      "text": "happening all at once,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 562743.0,
      "end_time": 565150.0,
      "text": "and we can ask much more interesting questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 565150.0,
      "end_time": 569774.0,
      "text": "How do air pollution and climate coexist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 569774.0,
      "end_time": 571283.0,
      "text": "Can we change things"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 571283.0,
      "end_time": 573872.0,
      "text": "that affect air pollution and climate at the same time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 573872.0,
      "end_time": 576216.0,
      "text": "The answer is yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 576216.0,
      "end_time": 579260.0,
      "text": "So this is a history of the 20th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 579260.0,
      "end_time": 581503.0,
      "text": "The first one is the model."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 581503.0,
      "end_time": 582910.0,
      "text": "The weather is a little bit different"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 582910.0,
      "end_time": 584199.0,
      "text": "to what actually happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 584199.0,
      "end_time": 586231.0,
      "text": "The second one are the observations."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 586231.0,
      "end_time": 588556.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re going through the 1930s."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 588556.0,
      "end_time": 591380.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s variability, there are things going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 591380.0,
      "end_time": 593562.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s all kind of in the noise."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 593562.0,
      "end_time": 596424.0,
      "text": "As you get towards the 1970s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 596424.0,
      "end_time": 598433.0,
      "text": "things are going to start to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 598433.0,
      "end_time": 600495.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to start to look more similar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 600495.0,
      "end_time": 603530.0,
      "text": "and by the time you get to the 2000s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 603630.0,
      "end_time": 605705.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re already seeing the patterns of global warming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 605705.0,
      "end_time": 608454.0,
      "text": "both in the observations and in the model."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 608454.0,
      "end_time": 610580.0,
      "text": "We know what happened over the 20th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 610581.0,
      "end_time": 612341.0,
      "text": "Right? We know that it&#39;s gotten warmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 612341.0,
      "end_time": 613952.0,
      "text": "We know where it&#39;s gotten warmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 613952.0,
      "end_time": 616692.0,
      "text": "And if you ask the models why did that happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 616692.0,
      "end_time": 618817.0,
      "text": "and you say, okay, well, yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 618817.0,
      "end_time": 620683.0,
      "text": "basically it&#39;s because of the carbon dioxide"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 620683.0,
      "end_time": 622662.0,
      "text": "we put into the atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 622662.0,
      "end_time": 624344.0,
      "text": "We have a very good match"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 624344.0,
      "end_time": 626971.0,
      "text": "up until the present day."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 626971.0,
      "end_time": 630391.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s one key reason why we look at models,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 630391.0,
      "end_time": 632612.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s because of this phrase here."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 632612.0,
      "end_time": 635107.0,
      "text": "Because if we had observations of the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 635107.0,
      "end_time": 638435.0,
      "text": "we obviously would trust them more than models,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 638436.0,
      "end_time": 640380.0,
      "text": "But unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 640380.0,
      "end_time": 645920.0,
      "text": "observations of the future are not available at this time."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 645920.0,
      "end_time": 648625.0,
      "text": "So when we go out into the future, there&#39;s a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 648625.0,
      "end_time": 651187.0,
      "text": "The future is unknown, the future is uncertain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 651187.0,
      "end_time": 653591.0,
      "text": "and there are choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 653591.0,
      "end_time": 655424.0,
      "text": "Here are the choices that we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 655424.0,
      "end_time": 657563.0,
      "text": "We can do some work to mitigate"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 657563.0,
      "end_time": 660358.0,
      "text": "the emissions of carbon dioxide into the atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 660358.0,
      "end_time": 662284.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the top one."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 662284.0,
      "end_time": 664189.0,
      "text": "We can do more work"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 664190.0,
      "end_time": 666366.0,
      "text": "to really bring it down"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 666366.0,
      "end_time": 668584.0,
      "text": "so that by the end of the century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 668584.0,
      "end_time": 671480.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not much more than there is now."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 671480.0,
      "end_time": 674815.0,
      "text": "Or we can just leave it to fate"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 674815.0,
      "end_time": 676308.0,
      "text": "and continue on"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 676308.0,
      "end_time": 680540.0,
      "text": "with a business-as-usual type of attitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 680540.0,
      "end_time": 683510.0,
      "text": "The differences between these choices"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 683510.0,
      "end_time": 688307.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t be answered by looking at models."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 688307.0,
      "end_time": 689946.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a great phrase"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 689946.0,
      "end_time": 691739.0,
      "text": "that Sherwood Rowland,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 691739.0,
      "end_time": 695603.0,
      "text": "who won the Nobel Prize for the chemistry"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 695603.0,
      "end_time": 697876.0,
      "text": "that led to ozone depletion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 697876.0,
      "end_time": 700273.0,
      "text": "when he was accepting his Nobel Prize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 700273.0,
      "end_time": 701652.0,
      "text": "he asked this question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 701652.0,
      "end_time": 703963.0,
      "text": "\"What is the use of having developed a science"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 703963.0,
      "end_time": 707223.0,
      "text": "well enough to make predictions if, in the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 707224.0,
      "end_time": 710530.0,
      "text": "all we&#39;re willing to do is stand around"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 710530.0,
      "end_time": 712760.0,
      "text": "and wait for them to come true?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 712760.0,
      "end_time": 715497.0,
      "text": "The models are skillful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 715497.0,
      "end_time": 718814.0,
      "text": "but what we do with the information from those models"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 718815.0,
      "end_time": 720986.0,
      "text": "is totally up to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 720986.0,
      "end_time": 722924.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 722924.0,
      "end_time": 725840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}